Markel-Gayner Asset Management Corporation: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 24, 2017 3:15 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Markel-Gayner Asset Management Corporation



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Markel-Gayner Asset Management Corporation is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to individuals, high net worth individuals, corporations and other businesses, and insurance companies. It manages separate client focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm invests in equity and fixed income markets of the United States. It employs fundamental analysis to create its portfolios. The firm obtains external research to complement its in-house research to make its investments. It was founded in December 1990 and is based in Glen Allen, Virginia. Markel-Gayner Asset Management Corporation operates as a subsidiary of Markel Corporation.


4521 Highwoods ParkwayGlen Allen, VA 23060United StatesFounded in 1990



Phone: 804-527-3806

